Class CardHierarchy

  • java.lang.Object
    • pl.edu.agh.kis.pz1.util.CardHierarchy
  • public class CardHierarchy
extends java.lang.Object
    Class used for Player's hand estimation. Provides the methods necessary to check which hand ranking hierarchy combination Player has, if any.
